{"tid":1516684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想問保護記者基金去左邊","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T05:32:39.000Z","uid":165683,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"aa319e79732dc1ea7f3ce99806d4c321b36864de","tid":1516684,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkjaraisefund/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkjaraisefund%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkKZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=1589a525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkjaraisefund/</a><br />\n籌左300萬去左邊<br />\n依家佢地keep 住影響新聞自由點解可以由佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKxBwZR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKxBwZR.png&h=d3ff41b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56263d9c81609737a053a7be9eada04834b12173","tid":1516684,"uid":231818,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"d70854ed2b291dfb8e05a8b6c6aab5b353532b51","tid":1516684,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:53:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4c5c64281758f6c8e728f73eb2e30f6b7010d680","tid":1516684,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"[置頂-連登改變世界]929全球集會抗赤納粹，召喚攬炒巴，G20巴，動畫巴，各文宣巴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n孫子兵法：求其上，得其中；求其中，得其下；求其下，必敗。<br />\n上：中共<br />\n中：林鄭<br />\n下：警犬"},{"pid":"bc4d07c93d93da0e4738a692deee9882